data.description: Welcome to this stunning home in Village Green Estates with all the bells and whistles!  This home features gorgeous hardwoods throughout the main living area, upgraded molding throughout, primary on main, coffered ceilings, large gourmet kitchen with granite counters, double oven, huge pantry, drop zone, office, second living room upstairs, two sets of Jack-n-Jill baths, large laundry, very spacious secondary bedrooms, tall ceilings throughout the home, beautiful firepit, fenced in backyard and so much more!
